     * Possible values: MediaBox, CropBox, TrimBox, BleedBox, ArtBox<br />
     * Default value: CropBox<br />
     * <br />
     * <b>PrintArea</b> <i>(string)</i><br />
     * Possible values: MediaBox, CropBox, TrimBox, BleedBox, ArtBox<br />
     * Default value: CropBox<br />
     * <br />
     * <b>PrintClip</b> <i>(string)</i><br />
     * Possible values: MediaBox, CropBox, TrimBox, BleedBox, ArtBox<br />
     * Default value: CropBox.<br />
     * <br />
